data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Walkers Woods subdivision within the sought-after Carolina Forest community! This established community in the fastest growing area of Myrtle Beach has tree lined streets, sidewalks and does not have that cookie cutter feel. This stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.   Step inside and immediately be impressed by the brand new luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring that graces the main floor. The modern and durable LVP flooring not only adds a touch of elegance but also ensures easy maintenance for years to come. It's the perfect backdrop for your everyday life and entertaining guests.  Upstairs, you'll discover new carpeting throughout the second floor, providing a plush and cozy atmosphere. Whether it's a quiet retreat in one of the spacious bedrooms or a family movie night in the bonus room, you'll find this home offers a seamless blend of aesthetics and comfort.  Nestled on a generously sized lot, this property offers ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding in your hot tub while taking in the scenery. The backyard is a haven for relaxation and recreation, making it an ideal setting for summer barbecues or creating your own oasis.  Location, location, location! Walkers Woods it's a gateway to the best of the Carolina Forest lifestyle. Enjoy the convenience of being a stone's throw away from shopping, a diverse array of restaurants, championship golf courses, and cutting-edge hospital systems, making healthcare access a breeze. All this and add in the bonus of being 10 minutes to the Atlantic Ocean and our beautiful Grand Strand beaches...but keep reading there's more...  Families will appreciate the proximity to award-winning schools within walking distance, ensuring your children have an excellent education. It's a community that caters to all your needs, whether it's work, play, or education.  Call and speak with the listing agent directly to discuss financing options that will save you HUNDREDS / month too!!!! If you're in the market for a house, then NOW is the time you were meant to see this home come across your screen.
